ON BOOK CONTENT AND TAKEDOWN REQUESTS

The methodologies in this repository are summarized and adapted from
published books. The full attribution policy, list of public sources used,
and the takedown procedure (24-hour response, no lawyer needed) are
documented in README.md under "版权与基于公开内容的说明".

If you are a rights holder and have concerns about any skill in this
repository, please file a GitHub issue or email zhichao1208@gmail.com
with subject "[Takedown] <Book Title>".
